<p><ent>Birr</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Birr
<hw>Birr</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A whirring sound, as of a
spinning wheel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A rush or impetus; force.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Birrus</ent>⟦br⟧
